reviewText: So glad I purchased this! This is the best show with Melanie and Derwin! I don't watch the new episodes because they're not it but I do enjoy re-re-watching these episodes. They're hilarious!
I am glad that I purchased these.  This is when THE GAME was a real show and worth watching.
I love every single one of these seasons.  I loved all the characters and can't wait to watch Season 6 this weekend.
This show is totally addictive. I am pleased to have found all of the first 5 seasons at such a great price. Love it!!
I was super excited about receiving this set. Im very satistified with the quality and finally got to catch up on my fav show..
